il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser.kb

Class GraphKbWithSempreTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser.kb.GraphKbWithSempreTypes

  • public class GraphKbWithSempreTypes
extends java.lang.Object
    A KB that represents relations and entities as NameValue and Value objects. Note: an instance of this class may contain more data than a GraphKb, such as the order of entities in a field list. Implementation note: the data structures in this class where chosen to allow efficient access during inference.
